# ============================================================================
# DysonianLineCNN .gitignore
# Rule of thumb: code and configs in git, data and artifacts in Google Drive.
# ============================================================================

# --- Data (never commit; lives in Google Drive) ---
*.npy
*.mat
data/*/*.DTA
data/*/*.DSC

# --- Legacy flat data/ (pre-multi-set) ---
data/*.DTA
data/*.DSC

# --- Derived baseline fitter outputs ---
data/*_fit_*.png

# --- Training artifacts (live in Google Drive under runs/) ---
runs/

# --- Per-spectrum inference artifacts at project root ---
/*_spectrum.csv
/*_spectrum_preview.png
/*_cnn_fit.png
/*_real_predicted_params.json

# --- Results: per-spectrum JSONs and PNGs are gitignored ---
# Summary CSVs (summary.csv, comparison.csv) ARE committed.
results/*/matlab/*_fit.json
results/*/matlab/*_fit.png
results/*/easyspin/*_fit.json
results/*/easyspin/*_fit.png
results/*/cnn/*_predicted.json
results/*/cnn/*_cnn_fit.png

# --- Archive of old/unclear files ---
bin/

# --- User-specific config (absolute paths, personal) ---
config/paths.json

# --- Internal dev docs (not part of the published article) ---
# redacted.md is meta-context for redacted Code sessions, MigrationPlan.md is
# the historical refactor plan. Both stay on disk locally for ongoing work
# but are not part of the public code drop. They will be filter-branched
# out of git history as part of the pre-public audit.
redacted.md
MigrationPlan.md

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
venv/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Jupyter ---
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Editors / IDE ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# --- macOS ---
.DS_Store

# --- redacted Code session state ---
.redacted/
